# 🐾 Pet Adoption API (MongoDB + Express)

A full-featured REST API for managing adoptable pets using **Node.js**, **Express.js**, and **MongoDB** with **Mongoose** ODM.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Modular route handling with `express.Router()`
- Connects to MongoDB Atlas or local MongoDB
- Add, list, and search pets by name
- Input validation and 404 error handling
- Environment variable support via `.env`

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
- dotenv

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

PET ADOPTION API/
├── models/
│ └── Pet.js # Mongoose schema & model
├── routes/
│ └── pet.js # API routes
├── .env # MongoDB URI
├── index.js # Entry point
├── package.json
└── README.md
